SUMMARY:IMPROMPTU LI - C1 will like this (25F)
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Bicycle Club (LBC) Meetup\n## Details\n\nRide Leader
 : Bruce Black\n\nAn enjoyable ride west and north of Lititz with very litt
 le climbing. This was my attempt to keep it below 1000' of climbing. We wi
 ll stop at Zig's for food/beverage. The pace will be 14 - 16 mph average. 
 Multiple regroup points. Please park in the upper parking lot of the libra
 ry.\n\nThis ride is a social ride\, but cyclists are not expected to stay 
 in one group. Cyclists may pedal at their own comfortable paces. Please be
  supportive of the other cyclists to avoid anyone biking alone or being dr
 opped off the back of the last group.\n\nCue and Ride with GPS links:\n[ht
 tps://ridewithgps.com/routes/52524059](https://ridewithgps.com/routes/5252
 4059)\n\nHelmets are mandatory\; please also plan to bring 1-2 water bottl
 es\, and a basic repair kit (spare tube\, tire levers\, pump/CO2 inflator)
 .\nBeing a Meetup Member does not mean you are a club member. Use this lin
 k to join the club.\n[https://www.lancasterbikeclub.net/content.aspx?page_
 id=60&club_id=257148](https://www.lancasterbikeclub.net/content.aspx?page_
 id=60&club_id=257148)\nYour RSVP is your agreement to abide by the club's 
 Code of Conduct [https://lancbikeclub.clubexpress.com/content.aspx?page_id
 =22&club_id=257148&module_id=323984](https://lancbikeclub.clubexpress.com/
 content.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=323984)\nand Rules of the
  Road\n[https://lancbikeclub.clubexpress.com/content.aspx?](https://lancbi
 keclub.clubexpress.com/content.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=32
 5159)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/lancaster-bicycle-club/events/3137754
 88/
